= Requirements

- OS: ubuntu, debian

= Overview

This module install and configure polipo for disk caching. It doesn't clear
it's cache (/var/cache/polipo), so it's perfect for pip/buildout/gem builders,
who downloads again and again the same files.

== Parameters

None. Defaults are marvelous. Even config files are not provided by this module.

= Usage

node "..." {
  include polipo
}

